com.github.katjahahn.parser.optheader

Enum WindowsEntryKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<WindowsEntryKey>
      • com.github.katjahahn.parser.optheader.WindowsEntryKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HeaderKey, OptionalHeaderKey, FieldOrStructureKey, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<WindowsEntryKey>

    public enum WindowsEntryKey
extends java.lang.Enum<WindowsEntryKey>
implements OptionalHeaderKey
    Represents a windows specific field from the optional header.

    Descriptions are taken from the PECOFF specification.
